Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,

<% case @notification.notification_type %>
<% when "shift_reminder" %>
Reminder: Your upcoming shift "<%= @data["shift_title"] %>" on <%= @data["shift_date"] %>.
<% when "hour_approved" %>
Your <%= @data["hours"] %> hours for <%= @data["program_name"] %> have been approved.
<% when "hour_rejected" %>
Your hours submission requires attention. Please log in to review.
<% when "milestone_reached" %>
Congratulations on reaching the "<%= @data["milestone_label"] %>" milestone!
<% when "credential_expiry" %>
Your credential "<%= @data["credential_name"] %>" expires in <%= @data["days_until_expiry"] %> days.
<% when "broadcast" %>
<%= @data["subject"] %>

<%= @data["body"] %>
<% when "announcement" %>
New announcement: <%= @data["title"] %>
Log in to read it.
<% when "inactivity_nudge" %>
We miss you! It's been a while since your last volunteer session.
Check out upcoming opportunities at <%= root_url %>.
<% else %>
You have a new notification. Log in to your dashboard: <%= root_url %>
<% end %>

—
<%= @organisation.name %>
